      "text": "両足の靴紐をこっそり結んでおいたゲシよ！",
      "startTime": 21.6578891079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "無様な転びっぷりやなぁ、あんちゃん……",
      "startTime": 25.6912223378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-smr001.wav",
      "text": "ちょっとボケっとし過ぎとちゃいますか？",
      "startTime": 29.957889235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうゲシ！　ボケっとしてないで",
      "startTime": 34.0578884958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-skr002.wav",
      "text": "早く私達にBIG4の仕事を用意しろゲシ！",
      "startTime": 36.5912225683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんて無駄に邪悪なんだ……！　というか仕事って",
      "startTime": 40.6912220834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-koh003.wav",
      "text": "まさかさくら達の仕事をかわりにやる気なのか！？",
      "startTime": 44.7666666627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私達がBIG4なんだから当たり前ゲシ！　おいバルゴ",
      "startTime": 48.2029002387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-skr003.wav",
      "text": "お前に仕事を管理する任務を与えるゲシ！",
      "startTime": 53.436234057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "十七歳に重大任務！　ぴちぴち十代、ひらめいた！",
      "startTime": 57.002896424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-hrk001.wav",
      "text": "まずは『ラジオ収録』で世界掌握！　チェケラ！",
      "startTime": 61.736234057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（くそっ、さくら達の大事な仕事を……！）",
      "startTime": 66.2362279771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
